{"tid":1725391,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"致罷唔到工嘅你","createTime":"2019-11-15T17:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T04:08:27.000Z","uid":61161,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"191273aa485d29d5ad63c5da5d0f660b69130c64","tid":1725391,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:31:29.000Z","msg":"我知道大家都有顧慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔割，但你可以將罷唔到工嘅日子<br />\n將果一日糧捐助比有需要嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者半日糧都好（自行計算）<br />\n你哋嘅資金積少成多<br />\n係可以做到好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36059c09941d7752e5cb3a0d32a1c48b769aec7","tid":1725391,"uid":188907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:38:31.000Z","msg":"其實好明白<br />\n<br />\n老實講 我都要養家交租<br />\n已經成日發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日頭返工 中午和你lunch 夜晚開花<br />\n攰到7個1皮<br />\n<br />\n我見到手足中槍 有罷<br />\n85有罷<br />\n大三罷有罷<br />\n<br />\n再罷落去我連養自己都冇錢 點捐去星火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但如果手足堅持，我都會繼續支持<br />\n要留守，我會送物資<br />\n要開花 我即刻去<br />\n要街坊 我換裝即刻變街坊撚狗都得<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係大家齊心 唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06266c8dcee1425ffe55ee924ba404a0a0a7e2e","tid":1725391,"uid":60338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:08:27.000Z","msg":"Dji28000<br />\n我由年中沽到輸左身家<br />\n嗚嗚嗚<br />\n唔該樓主以後唔好再扮專家"}]}